<section id="benefits" class="section">
  <div class="container benefits-container">
    <div class="badge section-badge">Membership Benefits</div>
    <h2 class="h2">Why Smart Investors <br />Choose HODL Alpha</h2>
    <p class="muted section-lead">
      Transform your investment approach with our algorithmic buy alerts &amp; access to our open
      HODL Alpha portfolio
    </p>

    <div class="benefits">
      <article class="benefit">
        <div class="benefit-icn">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"
            ><path fill="currentColor" d="M3 3h2v18H3zM8 13h2v8H8zM13 9h2v12h-2zM18 5h2v16h-2z"
            ></path></svg
          >
        </div>
        <div>
          <h4 class="benefit-title">Proven Performance</h4>
          <p class="muted benefit-copy">
            Backtested, our system has consistently outperformed returns vs the traditional DCA buy
            and hold strategy every single year since Bitcoin's inception in 2011.
          </p>
        </div>
      </article>

      <article class="benefit">
        <div class="benefit-icn">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"
            ><path
              fill="currentColor"
              d="M12 12a5 5 0 1 0-5-5a5 5 0 0 0 5 5m0 2c-4 0-8 2-8 5v1h16v-1c0-3-4-5-8-5"
            ></path></svg
          >
        </div>
        <div>
          <h4 class="benefit-title">Portfolio Entry Alerts</h4>
          <p class="muted benefit-copy">
            Get live access to our portfolio &amp; instant text / email alerts on every buy entry —
            you’ll always know exactly when we’re adding to our HODL position.
          </p>
        </div>
      </article>

      <article class="benefit">
        <div class="benefit-icn">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"
            ><path fill="currentColor" d="M11 2v20a9 9 0 0 1 0-20m2 0a9 9 0 0 1 0 20z"></path></svg
          >
        </div>
        <div>
          <h4 class="benefit-title">Live Portfolio Reviews</h4>
          <p class="muted benefit-copy">
            Join us as we review the entire portfolio and recent entries via live Zoom call every
            quarter.
          </p>
        </div>
      </article>

      <article class="benefit">
        <div class="benefit-icn">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"
            ><path fill="currentColor" d="M16 11V7h-2v4h-2l3 3l3-3zM6 3h12v2H6zm-2 4h16v14H4z"
            ></path></svg
          >
        </div>
        <div>
          <h4 class="benefit-title">Quantified Algorithmic Strategy</h4>
          <p class="muted benefit-copy">
            Our strategies are quantified which removes guesswork. The algo runs the rules and
            triggers the alerts.
          </p>
        </div>
      </article>

      <article class="benefit">
        <div class="benefit-icn">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"
            ><path fill="currentColor" d="m12 1l3 7l7 1l-5 5l1 7l-6-3l-6 3l1-7l-5-5l7-1z"
            ></path></svg
          >
        </div>
        <div>
          <h4 class="benefit-title">Transparency</h4>
          <p class="muted benefit-copy">
            We keep a live ledger of the entire portfolio: every position, every move, overall
            performance and individual entries.
          </p>
        </div>
      </article>

      <article class="benefit">
        <div class="benefit-icn">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"
            ><path
              fill="currentColor"
              d="M12 1a11 11 0 1 0 11 11A11.013 11.013 0 0 0 12 1m1 6v5l4 2l-1 1l-5-3V7z"
            ></path></svg
          >
        </div>
        <div>
          <h4 class="benefit-title">Early Access to new Portfolios</h4>
          <p class="muted benefit-copy">
            Members get early access to future portfolios before the general public.
          </p>
        </div>
      </article>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .benefits-container {
    margin-top: -100px;
    text-align: center;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
  }
  .section-badge {
    letter-spacing: 0.3em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--accent);
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }
  .benefits-container .h2 {
    margin: 12px 0 0;
    font-size: clamp(2.25rem, 3vw, 3.25rem);
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
  }
  .section-lead {
    margin-top: 18px;
    max-width: 720px;
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }
  .benefits {
    margin-top: clamp(32px, 5vw, 64px);
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    width: 100%;
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .benefit {
    padding: clamp(28px, 4vw, 48px) clamp(24px, 4vw, 40px);
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    text-align: center;
    gap: 20px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
  }
  .benefit:last-child {
    border-bottom: none;
  }
  .benefit-icn {
    display: grid;
    place-items: center;
    width: 72px;
    height: 72px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.12);
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.04);
  }
  .benefit-icn svg {
    width: 36px;
    height: 36px;
    color: white;
  }
  .benefit-title {
    margin: 0;
    font-size: 1.3rem;
    color: var(--accent);
    font-weight: 700;
  }
  .benefit-copy {
    margin: 0;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }
  @media (min-width: 720px) {
    .section-lead {
      font-size: 1.1rem;
    }
  }
  @media (min-width: 960px) {
    .benefits {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, minmax(0, 1fr));
    }
    .benefit {
      border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
      border-right: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
    }
    .benefit:nth-child(3n) {
      border-right: none;
    }
    .benefit:nth-last-child(-n + 3) {
      border-bottom: none;
    }
  }
</style>
